cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.NE 

This paper is about few-shot learning, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper proposes a novel approach to adapt the embedding model to the target classification task, which involves attention mechanisms (cs.AI) and natural language processing techniques (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper uses neural networks (cs.NE) to implement the proposed approach.
